{"tid":2235124,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"宣道校友家長聯署登頭版 聲援遭停牌教師 斥教局罔顧學生利益","createTime":"2020-10-08T12:02:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T05:15:43.000Z","uid":240362,"like":53,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"e5615ab6ab39d05d8e6b5f6b718464b4704d9a43","tid":2235124,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T12:02:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/xNyAxeWLVaeFMX3OKzlihLYyT2w=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TC4BU34BYFAZTG3HKLA4K6QKGE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FxNyAxeWLVaeFMX3OKzlihLYyT2w%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTC4BU34BYFAZTG3HKLA4K6QKGE.png&h=9f6116a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九龍塘宣道小學一名教師早前被教育局指「有計劃地散播港獨信息」而釘牌，外界質疑教育局以言入罪，製造白色恐怖 。有該校舊生及學生家長發起聯署聲援涉事教師，並決定在明日《蘋果》登頭版廣告力撐學校。有協助發起聯署及捐款登報的校友批評，教育局刻意扭曲涉事教師的教學本意，推翻學校調查的理據亦不清晰。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Dp0binwpZq0CaV4Pj1S_uzRdIPk=/802x1170/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/A4S5ENJ2FZBEDBZ7Q43L3B2ODY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FDp0binwpZq0CaV4Pj1S_uzRdIPk%3D%2F802x1170%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FA4S5ENJ2FZBEDBZ7Q43L3B2ODY.png&h=51176d5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201008/5OKHEBZAYRFXPI54IEUXFXAJLU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201008%2F5OKHEBZAYRFXPI54IEUXFXAJLU%2F&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusr4m5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=e14cc895\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201008%2F5OKHEBZAYRFXPI54IEUXFXAJLU%2F&h=a6ebc9de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.app